no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/gm-delays-production-of-chevy-silverado-equinox-and-gmc-sierra-evs-165609448.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/gm-delays-production-of-chevy-silverado-equinox-and-gmc-sierra-evs-165609448.html"><ins>推迟使用其 Ultium 电池组的电动汽车的生产</ins></a>，包括 Equinox、Silverado 和 GMC Sierra 电动汽车。作为现已取消的本田平价电动汽车计划的一部分，两家公司打算开发基于 Ultium 的小型跨界 SUV 以与特斯拉竞争。</p><p>这只是本田和通用汽车一直在合作的几个项目之一，它的解散似乎不会对其他项目产生任何影响。几天前，两家公司宣布将与 Cruise 合作，于 2026 年在日本推出无人驾驶乘车服务。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/honda-and-gm-have-given-up-on-their-plan-to-co-create-affordable-evs-154535464.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/honda-and-gm-have-given-up-on-their-plan-to-co-create-affordable-evs-154535464.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4107ea2c-c99a-4c6f-86b0-b5b54c211b08</guid><dc:creator>夏安·麦克唐纳</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 15:45:35 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1698248154</ingested><modified> 2023-10-25T15:35:58+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Transportation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Cheyenne MacDonald]]></category><media:content height="2937" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/67c51f10-734a-11ee-bbc7-8e39f5639437" width="4385"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2937" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-image