4-163048135.html"><ins>启发了即将推出的动画系列，这是有原因的。</ins></a>如果你在过去五年里一直持观望态度，并且拥有 Netflix 帐户，那么这是理所当然的。</p><p>该流媒体的“Netflix and Thrills”活动还发布了独立热门游戏<em>《Slayaway Camp》的全新续集，</em>该续集已于今天发布。至于电视和电影，该公司的传统支柱，“Netflix and Thrills”包括迈克·弗拉纳根 (Mike Flanagan) 的《厄<em>舍屋的倒塌》(The Fall of the House of Usher)、</em> UFO 纪录片系列《遭遇》( <em>Encounters)</em>和生存惊悚片《<em>无处》(Nowhere)</em>等。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/dead-cells-netflix-edition-scares-its-way-to-a-halloween-release-date-152630472.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/dead-cells-netflix-edition-scares-its-way-to-a-halloween-release-date-152630472.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 1718753a-13b9-4848-b3be-e0c95c0973c7</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 25 Oct 2023 15:26:30 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1698247590</ingested><modified> 2023-10-25T15:26:41+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="710" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/6b74fd20-7349-11ee-90f7-136dfba5bc5b" width="1270"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="710" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-10/6b74fd20-7349-11ee-90f7-136d